Subject: PowerBI Packs
Description:
Hello

Can you provide me with a link to download the Power BI Report Pack for Active Directory and Filesystem.

I have looked on the website and product pages but couldnt find it.

Thanks
Warren
What_We_Know__c:
The customer wants to know, from where they can download Power BI packs:

To download the Power BI Report Pack for FileSystem and Active Directory:
Login to Netwrix Customer Portal (Sign In)
Navigate to Netwrix Access Analyzer and expand it by clicking on "Download" button.
Afterwards, click on "Version Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Add-ons".
In there, you will see the Power BI packs for download.
Solution_Comment__c:
Query
You wanted to get the link to download the Power BI Report Pack for Active Directory and Filesystem.

Solution
To download the Power BI Report Pack for File System and Active Directory:
Login to Netwrix Customer Portal (Sign In)
Navigate to Netwrix Access Analyzer and expand it by clicking on "Download" button.
Afterwards, click on "Version Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Add-ons".
In there, you will see the Power BI packs for download.
